# 
# We truncate the tables so we have a clean place to start from
# We then add all the variables that we will need for a clean unee-t v2.0 installation
# only 1 test product (and all the items needed: classification, component, version, milestone)
# only 1 user
#
# 
# We also create the generic Flags there too for the TEST product
